trans-unit.source: Represents a dialog box that allows the user to choose a type.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma caixa de diálogo que permite que o usuário escolha um tipo.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: This class prompts the user to browse a list of Windows Workflow Foundation and .NET Framework namespaces and their contained types and select a single type.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe solicita ao usuário para procurar uma lista de namespaces do Windows Workflow Foundation e do .NET Framework e seus tipos independentes e selecionar um único tipo.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> from which the dialog obtains services.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> do qual a caixa diálogo obtém serviços.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> from which to obtain type filtering services.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> do qual obter os serviços de filtragem de tipos.

trans-unit.source: The name of the selected type.
trans-unit.target: O nome do tipo selecionado.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> class by using an <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" />, and a string.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> usando um <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, um <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> e uma cadeia de caracteres.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> from which to obtain services.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" /> do qual obter serviços.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> from which to obtain type filtering services.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" /> do qual obter os serviços de filtragem de tipos.

trans-unit.source: The name of the selected type.
trans-unit.target: O nome do tipo selecionado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" /> that allows access local assemblies to load in the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" /> que dá acesso aos assemblies locais a serem carregados na caixa de diálogo do navegador de tipos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> class by using an <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" />, a string, and a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" />.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> usando um <see cref="T:System.IServiceProvider" />, um <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ITypeFilterProvider" />, uma cadeia de caracteres e um <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.TypeProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type selected by the user in the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o tipo selecionado pelo usuário na caixa de diálogo do navegador de tipos.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> selected by the user in the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Type" /> selecionado pelo usuário na caixa de diálogo de navegador de tipo.

trans-unit.source: Gets the component to associate with the type browser dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o componente a ser associado à caixa de diálogo do navegador de tipos.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" /> to bind to the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" /> ligar para o <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.

trans-unit.source: If the property returns a valid value--anything other than a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic)--the component is added to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.
trans-unit.target: Se a propriedade retornará um valor válido – algo diferente de uma referência nula (`Nothing` no Visual Basic) – o componente é adicionado à <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade é necessária porque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implementa <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component?displayProperty=nameWithType> always returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Para <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component?displayProperty=nameWithType> sempre retorna uma referência nula (`Nothing` no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets the container to associate with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o contêiner a ser associado à caixa de diálogo do navegador de tipos.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IContainer" /> to associate with the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IContainer" /> a ser associado ao <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" />.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container> returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component> has not bound an <xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent> to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.
trans-unit.target: Se <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container> retorna uma referência nula (`Nothing` no Visual Basic), <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Component> não tiver associado uma <xref:System.ComponentModel.IComponent> para o <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>.

trans-unit.source: This method is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Este método é necessário porque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implementa <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container?displayProperty=nameWithType> always returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Para <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23Container?displayProperty=nameWithType> sempre retorna uma referência nula (`Nothing` no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the type browser dialog is in design mode.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se a caixa de diálogo do navegador de tipos está no modo de design.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> is in design mode; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog" /> estiver no modo de design; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: O padrão é <see langword="true" />.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade é necessária porque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implementa <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23DesignMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> always returns `true`.
trans-unit.target: Para <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23ComponentModel%23ISite%23DesignMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> sempre retorna `true`.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets name of the component associated with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o nome do componente associado com a caixa de diálogo do navegador de tipos.

trans-unit.source: The name of the component associated with the type browser dialog.
trans-unit.target: O nome do componente associado com a caixa de diálogo de navegador de tipo.

trans-unit.source: This property is required because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implements <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade é necessária porque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog> implementa <xref:System.ComponentModel.ISite>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of service object to retrieve.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Type" /> do objeto de serviço a ser recuperado.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the service object for the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Recupera o objeto de serviço do tipo especificado.

trans-unit.source: A service object of type <paramref name="serviceType" />, or a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic) if there is no service object of type <paramref name="serviceType" />.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto de serviço do tipo <paramref name="serviceType" /> ou uma referência nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic) se não houver nenhum objeto de serviço do tipo <paramref name="serviceType" />.

trans-unit.source: If `serviceType` is of type <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23IServiceProvider%23GetService%2A> returns a service object.
trans-unit.target: Se `serviceType` é do tipo <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ITypeProvider>, <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.TypeBrowserDialog.System%23IServiceProvider%23GetService%2A> retorna um objeto de serviço.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it returns a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, ele retornará uma referência nula (`Nothing` em Visual Basic).
